title: Lily of the Valley - Among the Shadows - goth rock
description:
Artist: Lily of the Valley
Album: Among the Shadows
Style: Goth Rock
Year: 2014
Label: Halotan Records
More Info: www.halotan.net

Lily of the Valley's style is eclectic as the band mixes guitars with electronic and cannot be assigned to a definite genre. The music can be described as goth rock with the centre of gravity in the rock part of it. 

On the electronic part the band skilfully uses synthetic sounds to create songs that could possibly work on the dancefloor as well. Warm female vocals are far from typical goth style of singing and add another layer to the style that is interesting and unique
